1958;;A Tale of Two Cities;;British;;Ralph Thomas;;Dirk Bogarde, Dorothy Tutin;;literary drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A_Tale_of_Two_Cities_(1958_film);;Sydney Carton, a drunken English lawyer, discovers that Charles Darnay, a man he once defended, is a French aristocrat trying to escape the French Revolution. While he envies the man over the love of a woman, Lucie Manette, his conscience is pricked and he resolves to help him escape the guillotine.